description:
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bank Healthcare Assistants - WE WANT YOU!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you value your work/life balance?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want more flexibility over your working pattern?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you able to help deliver high quality patient care?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If so, joining the Trust Bank may be just what you are looking for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for experienced&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Healthcare Assistants to join the Trust Temporary Staffing Bank.  If you are a student nurse or anyone currently studying towards a degree in the care sector, as long as you have completed your first placement, joining the bank as an HCA can be a great way to gain valuable knowledge and experience in acute clinical areas and give you the opportunity to work flexibly around your studies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Trust Bank provides cover to Torbay and South Devon NHS Foundation Trust. This incorporates the main acute hospital in Torbay and a number of community hospitals and day care units in and around the South Devon area.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;What we need from you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Minimum of 6 months current/recent experience of working in the care sector&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A professional and caring attitude&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reliability&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;What we can offer you&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible working patterns&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Weekly pay&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paid annual leave&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access to the NHS Pension Scheme&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Free training and development opportunities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Online self-booking system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opportunity to work in a variety of departments giving you further knowledge and experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Opportunity to develop Education and Training for Level 2 and 3 Diploma in Healthcare ( please not this is not funded but we will support you)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Torbay is known as the English Riviera and boasts award-winning beaches, stunning coastline and a famously warm climate. The location is one of the UK’s most beautiful areas with easy access to the region’s top beaches; Dartmoor; the South West Coast Path; walking; sailing; water sports; cycling and mountain biking. There are also a number of outstanding schools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are shortlisted, you will be invited to an online interview (date and time to be confirmed).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please take time to customise your personal statement to ensure it accurately reflects the position you are applying for, and that your application is checked for errors / omissions prior to submission.  We may experience high levels of applications for this vacancy and therefore recommend that you submit your application as early as possible in order to ensure it is considered if the vacancy is closed early.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The main delay in a recruitment process is often confirmation of Employment History or References. We would like to make you aware that if you are successful, the Trust requires contact details for referees who can confirm your employment and/or education for the last 3 years.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
